description: Sensual. Dimensional. Eyes tell all. Passion meets pleasure in a palette of 16 shadows in matte, shimmer, and glitter finishes. Featuring bestselling NARS favorites Laguna, Orgasm, and Taj Mahal, plus complementary shades in a range of matte neutrals, warm bronzes, and exotic pink tones. Intense pigments create a high-impact effect that lasts. Limited edition.
name: Summer Unrated
